Dependencies:
    GLFW3
    GLAD (included with source code)
    stb_image (included with source code)
    imgui (included with source code)

Compile:
    1. Install glfw and reflect its directory in Makefile (might be tricky but works on my mac)
    2. run make

Interact with program:
    W/A/S/D to navigate through the landscape
    Mouse motion to look around
    Menu to switch between different weathers (yet to be fulfilled)


What remains to be done:
1. fix rendering bugs, snowflakes do not show up as intended.
2. Stars during night does not show.
3. Fulfill the horizontal line with more trees or buildings.
4. Reorganize file strucuture.
